88.4	The_Alchemist_(novel)	The Alchemist (novel)	The Alchemist is a novel by Paulo Coelho first published in 1988. Originally written in Portuguese, it has been translated into 67 languages as of 2009. An allegorical novel, The Alchemist follows a young Andalusian shepherd named Santiago in his journey to Egypt, after having a recurring dream of finding treasure there.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c4/TheAlchemist.jpg/200px-TheAlchemist.jpg
